{"tid":1376430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」打online game, 除咗用雞蛋之外仲可以用咩？","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T11:55:40.000Z","uid":100143,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9c38e618cfad98da3a47c354946f9ca5a5bdbc","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"打online game想升科技樹，可以用啲乜遠攻？<br />\n<br />\n越千奇百怪越好<br />\n可能會有意想不到，效果絕佳的選擇？<br />\n大家一齊brainstorm下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該討論頁面所有嘢都千奇唔好係真實世界用呀<br />\n<br />\n掉親花花草草就唔好啦😉<br />\n係onlinegame入面玩下就好啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瑞典鹽醃鯡魚<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JEciodgNWRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJEciodgNWRU&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=691d4be0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JEciodgNWRU</a><br />\n<br />\n優點：臭到痴線<br />\n一旦掂到<br />\n佢件衫唔洗要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我擔心佢地會唔夠衫著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（就算有防毒<br />\n我相信佢地之後都唔會想著果套衫）<br />\n<br />\n缺點：自己友可能會中招先"},{"pid":"a87bcc1964b3ad16b402a798410f86b22a09040f","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e0f839c6ee67d599fa6f348cc9de423a8229762","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"2. 潤滑劑<br />\n<br />\n優點：就算佢地嘅裝扣死咗係對手，但至少會因為滑而用唔到力，落手冇咁重<br />\n<br />\n缺點：可能會跣親自己友"},{"pid":"7834337583b3b0ec5439fc163af2b48cfde814f4","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5435e7d613c03354740a82dcd4b1b5dc621b29c2","tid":1376430,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"臭魚成本高"},{"pid":"b9799240a59daa42e42489e2623761b4fcf6b342","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"3. Itching powder<br />\n超級痕粉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZMZfinBisQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZMZfinBisQ8&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=4f4cd7c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZMZfinBisQ8</a><br />\n<br />\n只要接觸到皮膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忍到熱同重<br />\n但係忍唔忍到痕呢？<br />\n唔知收工除衫嘅時候會唔會掂到呢？<br />\n後面嘅嘢請自行想像<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需要先測試下個威力"},{"pid":"c8c1dc56f06a7158ed7e3a967c185fb96a375467","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5435e7d613c03354740a82dcd4b1b5dc621b29c2","tid":1376430,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"臭魚成本高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"所以宜家brain storm下<br />\n有時望落好on9<br />\n但意外有用"},{"pid":"5818774e2288a920ea4e7cd2913758c10ef07971","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"cf7d170c72597464ed92b52e84afe48cb3823c2c","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"c3f1f9d3dfeff48b4c8a11cff14854d5ef0583bf","tid":1376430,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"冰粒"},{"pid":"279451df2e1bc80859ebb32d25795384cc840c06","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f1f9d3dfeff48b4c8a11cff14854d5ef0583bf","tid":1376430,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"冰粒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"點解？<br />\nExplain小小唔該？"},{"pid":"abc2c03f8cd4d17ca4959b9eba29d53a46f3418e","tid":1376430,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike